---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Brooklyn's Finest Artisan Cheesecakes" description="Dreher's Cheesecake - Handcrafted artisan cheesecakes and custom cakes, delivered fresh across all five NYC boroughs.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-cream to-cream-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="font-accent text-xl text-gold-dark italic mb-4">Est. 2019</p>
          <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-chocolate mb-6">
            A Brooklyn<br />
            <span class="text-gold">Original</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Baking memories, one dessert at a time. From our Brooklyn kitchen to your table, 
            every Dreher's creation is made with love, premium ingredients, and a whole lot of passion.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8">
            <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">
              Shop Our Collection
            </a>
            <a href="/how-we-work" class="btn btn-secondary">
              How We Work
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-gold">100+</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate">Happy Customers</p>
            </div>
            <div class="h-12 w-px bg-cream-dark"></div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-gold">5</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate">Star Rating</p>
            </div>
            <div class="h-12 w-px bg-cream-dark"></div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-gold">5</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate">NYC Boroughs</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/images/products/7c3b14e4-ba1b-4c6e-a1b6-003154d430a5.png" 
              alt="Dreher's Artisan Cheesecake" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-48 h-48 bg-gold rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="section-header">
          <p class="section-subtitle">Our Journey</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">The Dreher's Story</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg text-slate mx-auto">
          <p>
            What started as a passion for baking in our home kitchen has grown into 
            Brooklyn's beloved cheesecake destination. At Dreher's, we believe that 
            every dessert should be a celebration — a moment of pure joy shared with 
            the people you love.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Our journey began with a simple goal: to create the most delicious, 
            creamy, and memorable cheesecakes in New York. We experimented with 
            countless recipes, sourced the finest ingredients, and perfected our 
            craft through years of dedication.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Today, we're proud to offer a diverse menu of classic cheesecakes, 
            stunning custom cakes, and indulgent vegan options — all handcrafted 
            with the same love and attention to detail that started it all.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-chocolate text-cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="section-subtitle text-gold">What We Stand For</p>
        <h2 class="section-title text-cream">Our Values</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-gold" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.456 2.456zM16.894 20.567L16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 001.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 001.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423 1.423z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-gold mb-3">Quality First</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/80">
            We use only the finest ingredients — premium cream cheese, fresh fruits, 
            and real vanilla. No shortcuts, no compromises.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-gold" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-gold mb-3">Made with Love</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/80">
            Every cheesecake is handcrafted with care and attention. We put our 
            heart into every creation because we know it matters.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-gold" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-gold mb-3">Community First</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/80">
            We're proud to serve all five NYC boroughs. Our neighbors aren't just 
            customers — they're family.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-berry to-berry-light text-white">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ready to Order?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Whether it's a birthday, anniversary, or just because — let us make 
        your celebration sweeter with our handcrafted desserts.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/products" class="btn bg-white text-berry hover:bg-cream hover:text-berry-light">
          Shop Now
        </a>
        <a href="/how-we-work" class="btn border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-berry">
          Learn More
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
